fields.name: Assignment
fields.description: Configuration details of the guest configuration assignment.

fields.name: ComplianceStatus
fields.description: A value indicating compliance status of the machine for the assigned guest configuration.

fields.name: EndTime
fields.description: End date and time of the guest configuration assignment compliance status check.

fields.name: Id
fields.description: ARM resource id of the report for the guest configuration assignment.

fields.name: OperationType
fields.description: Type of report, Consistency or Initial

fields.name: ReportId
fields.description: GUID that identifies the guest configuration assignment report under a subscription, resource group.

fields.name: Resources
fields.description: The list of resources for which guest configuration assignment compliance is checked.

fields.name: StartTime
fields.description: Start date and time of the guest configuration assignment compliance status check.
